proof, non-chill filtered. Toasted pecan, dark caramel, a long ember finish.</p>\n        <div class=\"release-foot\">\n          <span class=\"release-price\">$64.99</span>\n          <span class=\"badge badge--success\">Bottling Oct 20</span>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"card card--lift\">\n        <span class=\"release-tag\">SINGLE CASK \u00b7 LOT 097</span>\n        <div class=\"release-name\">Coppersmith Reserve</div>\n        <p class=\"release-desc\">Seven-year single malt finished nine months in Oloroso sherry butts. Fig, waxed leather, forge-warm oak spice.</p>\n        <div class=\"release-foot\">\n          <span class=\"release-price\">$118.00</span>\n          <span class=\"badge badge--warning\">Awaiting labels</span>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"card card--lift\">\n        <span class=\"release-tag\">BOND SERIES \u00b7 NO. 7</span>\n        <div class=\"release-name\">Rickhouse Three</div>\n        <p class=\"release-desc\">Bottled-in-bond four grain, exactly 100 proof, one distilling season, one rickhouse. The house workhorse, done properly.</p>\n        <div class=\"release-foot\">\n          <span class=\"release-price\">$42.50</span>\n          <span class=\"badge badge--brand\">Blending</span>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ================= Footer ================= -->\n  <footer class=\"rise\">\n    <span>Copperline Distilling Co. \u2014 internal cask operations. Figures are demo data.</span>\n    <span class=\"mono\">FOUNDRY v1 \u00b7 RH-03 \u00b7 <a href=\"#\">ledger archive</a></span>\n  </footer>\n\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
